    <item>
      <title>雀巢首席执行官将增加营销支出，下调利润目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/nestle-reduces-its-profitability-target-will-split-off-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雀巢公司新任首席执行官 Laurent Freixe 计划增加营销支出，以恢复消费者对公司高价品牌的兴趣。此举将意味着中期盈利能力下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/nestle-reduces-its-profitability-target-will-split-off-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 06:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒂森克虏伯有望恢复盈利，推动扭亏为盈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/thyssenkrupp-tka-sees-negative-cash-flow-during-transition-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒂森克虏伯股份公司预计本财年将扭亏为盈，这表明包括重组陷入困境的钢铁部门在内的扭亏为盈计划正在取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/thyssenkrupp-tka-sees-negative-cash-flow-during-transition-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
