      <title>泰晤士水务公司推迟股权融资期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thames-water-pushes-deadline-in-hunt-for-3-3-billion-in-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司延长了寻求数十亿英镑新股权的最后期限，因为它要求潜在投资者提供更多帮助这家陷入困境的公用事业公司扭转局面的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thames-water-pushes-deadline-in-hunt-for-3-3-billion-in-equity</guid>
